      • invoke

        public void invoke​(net.dv8tion.jda.api.events.message.MessageReceivedEvent event,
                   java.lang.String messageText)
            throws AlyxException
        Invokes the command, passing any parameters to the command's method. If the parameters do not match the format of the method's parameters, the command's help text will instead by sent back to the user.
        Parameters:
        event - The Discord message event which triggered the command.
        messageText - The raw event message text, minus the command prefix.
        Throws:
        AlyxException - Exception thrown if invoking the command failed.
